# REALCal Bookings Consent Document

## Overview
By booking with REALCal Bookings, you consent to receiving transactional SMS and email notifications.

## Our Commitment
- We only send you booking-related information.
- We do not share your number or email with third parties for marketing.
- You can opt-out at any time.

## Verification
This document verifies your explicit opt-in to these communications as of the date of your booking.
